revised_prompt: Create a high-resolution, brightly lit, ethereal sports analytics dashboard background. The backdrop should be a vivid purple-blue gradient with radiating golden nebulae. Imagine bright and glowing, abstract data visualizations, such as floating translucent 3D bar charts, pie charts, and line graphs in bright gold and warm amber tones. Over this, lay bright holographic hexagonal grid patterns with a strong glow and luminous flowing data streams akin to bright golden constellations. Add very subtle silhouettes of wrestlers in action poses, barely visible in the brightly lit mist. Ensure you have floating numbers, such as 87, 342, 1249, 5.1, 106, 113, 120, 126, 132, in bright glowing gold with strong luminosity. Fashion bright trophy and medal icons with a considerable ethereal glow and radiant light beams. Add bright particle effects and luminous light streams. The overall atmosphere needs to be high in brightness and contrast, and luminous in nature. Do not add text or words; only numbers and visual elements are required. Draw inspiration from a bright modern dashboard UI background, luminous sports visualization, a bright theme with luxury gold accents, bright cinematic lighting, high key lighting, and a 4K resolution.
